
WaPOR Pipeline
=========================
Unified pipeline for downloading and processing WaPOR-3 dekadal rasters
(AETI and NPP), aggregating them into seasonal totals, and applying
per-crop masks to derive final yield estimates.

After masking, automatically computes 1st-percentile QC thresholds for
AETI and Yield (globally per crop per year) and saves them to
qc_thresholds.json in the output root. The statistics script reads this
file directly — no manual threshold entry needed.

Usage
-----
1. Edit the Config block at the bottom.
2. Run:  python wapor_yield_pipeline.py

Crops supported (2019)
----------------------
  cotton  | HI=0.45, MC=0.10, class=1
  paddy   | HI=0.47, MC=0.12, class=2
  redgram | HI=0.35, MC=0.10, class=3
"""


